query:
INSERT INTO workouts (title, slug, description, category, difficulty, duration, sport, targetMuscles, equipment, instructions, tips, caloriesBurned, featured) VALUES
('Full Body Power Workout', 'full-body-power-workout', 'Complete full body workout designed to build explosive power and strength. Perfect for athletes looking to improve overall performance.', 'Strength', 'intermediate', 45, 'All Sports', 'Full Body,Core,Legs,Arms', 'Dumbbells,Barbell,Pull-up Bar', '1. Warm up for 5 minutes
2. Squats: 4 sets x 10 reps
3. Deadlifts: 4 sets x 8 reps
4. Bench Press: 4 sets x 10 reps
5. Pull-ups: 3 sets x max reps
6. Planks: 3 sets x 60 seconds', 'Focus on form over weight. Rest 90 seconds between sets.', 450, 'yes'),
('Baseball Arm Care Routine', 'baseball-arm-care-routine', 'Essential arm care exercises for pitchers and position players. Prevent injuries and maintain arm health throughout the season.', 'Mobility', 'beginner', 20, 'Baseball', 'Shoulders,Rotator Cuff,Forearms', 'Resistance Bands,Light Dumbbells', '1. Band pull-aparts: 3x15
2. External rotations: 3x12 each arm
3. Prone Y-T-W: 2x10 each
4. Wrist curls: 3x15
5. Reverse wrist curls: 3x15', 'Do this routine before every throwing session.', 100, 'yes'),
('Football Speed & Agility', 'football-speed-agility', 'Explosive speed and agility drills designed for football players. Improve your 40-time and change of direction.', 'Speed', 'advanced', 35, 'Football', 'Legs,Core,Hip Flexors', 'Cones,Speed Ladder,Resistance Bands', '1. Dynamic warm-up: 5 min
2. Ladder drills: 4 variations x 3 reps
3. Cone drills: 5-10-5, L-drill, T-drill
4. Sprint intervals: 6x40 yards
5. Cool down stretches', 'Stay low in your athletic stance. Quick feet, quick hips.', 380, 'yes'),
('Basketball Vertical Jump', 'basketball-vertical-jump', 'Increase your vertical leap with this plyometric-focused workout. Dunk like a pro with consistent training.', 'Plyometrics', 'intermediate', 40, 'Basketball', 'Legs,Glutes,Calves', 'Box,Medicine Ball', '1. Box jumps: 4x8
2. Depth jumps: 3x6
3. Single-leg hops: 3x10 each
4. Squat jumps: 4x12
5. Calf raises: 4x20', 'Land softly and explode up immediately. Quality over quantity.', 320, 'no'),
('Core Strength for Athletes', 'core-strength-athletes', 'Build a rock-solid core that transfers power from your lower body to upper body. Essential for all athletes.', 'Core', 'intermediate', 25, 'All Sports', 'Abs,Obliques,Lower Back', 'Medicine Ball,Ab Wheel', '1. Planks: 3x60 sec
2. Russian twists: 3x20
3. Dead bugs: 3x12 each side
4. Ab wheel rollouts: 3x10
5. Side planks: 2x30 sec each', 'Brace your core like you are about to get punched.', 200, 'yes'),
('Recovery & Mobility Flow', 'recovery-mobility-flow', 'Active recovery session to improve flexibility, reduce soreness, and prepare your body for the next workout.', 'Recovery', 'beginner', 30, 'All Sports', 'Full Body,Hips,Shoulders', 'Foam Roller,Yoga Mat', '1. Foam rolling: 10 min full body
2. Hip flexor stretch: 2x30 sec each
3. Pigeon pose: 2x45 sec each
4. Cat-cow: 2x10
5. World greatest stretch: 2x5 each', 'Breathe deeply and relax into each stretch.', 120, 'no')
